condition.narrative: On-lending to PFIs shall be made only in accordance with the Eligibility Criteria, Terms and Conditions listed in Loan Agreement.

Section I.A.1 of Schedule 2 to the Loan AgreementThe Borrower shall, throughout the implementation of the Project, maintain itsProject Implementation Unit and ensure that said unit functions at all times in a manner and with staffing and budgetary resourcesnecessary and appropriate for implementation of the Project and satisfactory to the Bank.Effectiveness ConditionSection 6.01 ofthe Loan AgreementThe Borrower shall have adopted a revised Operational Manual satisfactory to the Bank.
Sub-financing to SMEs shall be made only in accordance with the Eligibility Criteria, Terms, Conditions and Approval Procedureslisted in Loan Agreement.
